    "is_free": false,
    "description": "塞壬森林是一款充满策略、冒险和挑战的roguelike游戏，您将探索神秘的森林，揭开里面深藏的秘密。游戏中提供海量技能组合、随机路线、多种结局等元素，让您在每一次的游戏中都能够享受到全新的体验。<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >上百种技能组合提供了极高的自由度</h2></li></ul></strong><br>你又一次被不知名的怪物击杀！好吧，这并不奇怪。你以为一把剑，一张被你揉搓过并带有，一个破洞的技能卡牌，还有一些防晒霜，驱蚊水就可以对付这些饥饿的小精灵和这片被黑暗地狱诅咒的森林吗？在提醒你一次！你是怎么挂掉的。你之前积攒的所有技能卡牌，都会丢失，重新进入游戏后，重新组合卡牌。然而，这些死亡并不像伟大的冒险家那样光荣和英勇-----它们是比较平庸的，缺乏任何史诗。没有关于它们的故事和传说(最多是几个小精灵的嘲笑和鄙视的笑声！！！！)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/6f6cc1752418b70b00e710c6b97c238b.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/6f6cc1752418b70b00e710c6b97c238b.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/6f6cc1752418b70b00e710c6b97c238b.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/d533894917209e41d3fd3b37742f192b.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/d533894917209e41d3fd3b37742f192b.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/d533894917209e41d3fd3b37742f192b.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机地图，多种结局</h2></li></ul></strong><br><br>也许你在树下眯一会，打了一个喷嚏，被巡逻的小精灵发现，砍死了！或许你行走在一片绿草地上，欣赏大自然的魅力的时候，却被突然钻出来的草爬爬给袭击了。你看似稳妥的行进路线，却隐藏着，巨大的危机。不管发生什么，死亡都过早地敲响了你的门，让你的荣耀之路戛然而止！<br>您的每一次探索都会随机生成不同的地图，收集宝藏、掌握技能卡，运用策略组合自己独特的技能套路。寻找最佳路线。每个地图都是独一无二的，充满了曲折的路线、危险、陷阱、随机事件！当然，还有宝藏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/610eaf2fa303c7c226467a531e78b848.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/610eaf2fa303c7c226467a531e78b848.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/610eaf2fa303c7c226467a531e78b848.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/ac371f40f805308d6d5fb8915e8b8a66.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/ac371f40f805308d6d5fb8915e8b8a66.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/ac371f40f805308d6d5fb8915e8b8a66.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >暗黑系列玩法和roguelike相结合</h2></li></ul></strong><br>在塞壬森林的世界里，每个死去的人最终都会回到迷雾聚集点，亡者之地。一个凌乱潮湿的地方，到处都是令人愤怒的黑心商人。这就是你走向荣耀之旅的开始！整理好你的装备，准备再次崛起，最终在这片迷雾世界里，留下你的传说或者成为这些小精灵茶余饭后谈论的又一个笑话！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/02b3fe8c7b29baf5856923f41275b981.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/02b3fe8c7b29baf5856923f41275b981.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/02b3fe8c7b29baf5856923f41275b981.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/4ed335d7319f886f39999fb17219c765.poster.avif?t=1695040704\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/4ed335d7319f886f39999fb17219c765.webm?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/4ed335d7319f886f39999fb17219c765.mp4?t=1695040704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <br><br><br><br>.........这就是你冒险开始的地方！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358350/extras/0fc03df9c6b46c627166db8a334f9369.avif?t=1695040704\" width=656 height=194 /></span>",
